to his loved ones.

243
00:18:56,310 --> 00:18:58,853
It’s a mighty good man
would go out of his way...

244
00:18:58,938 --> 00:19:01,981
to bring a word of cheer
to a grievin' widow.

245
00:19:02,066 --> 00:19:06,069
- [ Man ] So you ain't with the state no more?
- No, brother. I resigned only yesterday.

246
00:19:06,153 --> 00:19:09,697
