that laid his brother low.

253
00:19:27,466 --> 00:19:29,717
L-O-V-E.

254
00:19:29,802 --> 00:19:31,469
You see these fingers, dear hearts?

255
00:19:31,554 --> 00:19:34,472
These fingers has veins that run straight
to the soul of man.

256
00:19:34,557 --> 00:19:37,433
The right hand, friends -
the hand of love.

257
00:19:37,518 --> 00:19:39,477
Now watch and I'll show you
the story of life.

258
00:19:40,563 --> 00:19:44,566
These fingers, dear hearts, is always a-warrin'
and a-tuggin', one again' t'other.

259
00:19:44,650 --> 00:19:47,652
Now watch 'em.

260
00:19:47,736 --> 00:19:49,654
Old brother left hand.

261
00:19:49,738 --> 00:19:51,739
Left hand hate's a-fightin'.

262
00:19:51,824 --> 00:19:54,492
And it looks like love's a goner.

263
00:19:54,577 --> 00:19:57,328
But wait a minute. Wait a minute.

264
00:19:57,413 --> 00:19:59,789
Hot dog! Love's a-winnin'.

265
00:19:59,874 --> 00:20:02,167
Yes, sirree!

266
00:20:02,251 --> 00:20:04,169
It’s love that won.

267
00:20:04,253 --> 00:20:07,422
And old left hand hate
is down for the count.

268
00:20:09,175 --> 00:20:12,218
