336
00:23:51,730 --> 00:23:56,150
John!

337
00:24:06,161 --> 00:24:09,414
A woman's a fool to marry for that.
That's somethin' for a man.

338
00:24:09,498 --> 00:24:12,166
The good Lord never meant
for a decent woman to want that.

339
00:24:12,251 --> 00:24:14,502
Not really want it.

340
00:24:14,586 --> 00:24:18,423
It’s all just a fake and a pipe dream.
[ Chuckles ]

341
00:24:19,508 --> 00:24:22,260
John, Mr. Powell
has something to tell you.

342
00:24:25,013 --> 00:24:29,600
Well, John,
the night before your father died...

343
00:24:29,685 --> 00:24:32,186
