for me to let you know the news.

381
00:27:05,841 --> 00:27:10,553
Your mother told me she wanted me
to be a daddy to you and your sister.

382
00:27:10,637 --> 00:27:12,638
We're gonna get married, boy.

383
00:27:14,516 --> 00:27:16,934
Did you hear what I said, boy?

384
00:27:17,019 --> 00:27:18,853
- Ηmm?
- Married.

385
00:27:18,937 --> 00:27:22,815
We're goin' to Sisterville tomorrow,
and when we get back -

386
00:27:22,899 --> 00:27:26,652
You ain't my dad.
You'll never be my dad.

387
00:27:26,737 --> 00:27:30,281
When we get back,
we're all going to be friends...

388
00:27:30,365 --> 00:27:33,242
and share our fortunes together, John.

389
00:27:33,327 --> 00:27:36,704
You think you can make me tell!
But I won't! I won't! I won't!

390
00:27:36,788 --> 00:27:38,706
[ Gasps ]

391
00:27:39,708 --> 00:27:43,169
- Tell me what, boy?
- Nothin'.

392
00:27:43,962 --> 00:27:46,714
We're not keeping secrets
from each other, are we, little lad?

393
00:27:46,798 --> 00:27:49,008
No, no.

394
00:27:49,092 --> 00:27:52,094
[ Chuckles ]
Well, no matter.

395
00:27:53,221 --> 00:27:55,723
We've got a long time together, boy.

396
00:28:02,564 --> 00:28:05,650
[ Icey ]
Wave your hands. Great sakes.

397
00:28:05,734 --> 00:28:08,569
Now, you wait here
while I get your night things.

398
00:28:13,033 --> 00:28:16,535
- Now can I tell?
- Hmm?

399
00:28:16,620 --> 00:28:19,789
When Mr. Powell's our daddy,
then can I tell him about -

400
00:28:19,873 --> 00:28:21,832
- You swore, Pearl.
- John, don't.

401
00:28:21,917 --> 00:28:24,001
You promised Dad you wouldn't tell.

402
00:28:24,086 --> 00:28:27,088
I love Mr. Powell lots and lots, John.

403
00:28:58,537 --> 00:29:00,454
Men.

404
00:29:13,176 --> 00:29:15,386
Harry?

405
00:29:17,180 --> 00:29:19,181
Fix that window shade.

406
00:29:23,061 --> 00:29:24,562
[ Window Closes ]

407
00:29:29,151 --> 00:29:31,652
- Harry?
- I was praying.

408
00:29:33,321 --> 00:29:37,575
Oh, I'm sorry. I didn't know.
I - I thought -

409
00:29:37,659 --> 00:29:40,619
You thought, Willa, that the moment
you walked in that door...

410
00:29:40,704 --> 00:29:43,873
I'd start to pawin' you
in that abominable way...

411
00:29:43,957 --> 00:29:46,542
