465
00:33:22,717 --> 00:33:25,886
"Ye," said the Lord to that man...

466
00:33:25,971 --> 00:33:28,305
"you take that money...

467
00:33:28,390 --> 00:33:31,141
and you throw it in the river!"

468
00:33:31,226 --> 00:33:35,396
- In the river!
- In the river!

469
00:33:35,480 --> 00:33:37,481
