the dens of perdition where she dragged 'em.

1056
01:19:00,035 --> 01:19:03,871
Right funny, ain't it, how they rowed
all the way upriver in a 10-foot johnboat.

1057
01:19:05,624 --> 01:19:07,583
Are they well, Miz Cooper?

1058
01:19:07,668 --> 01:19:09,961
A sight better than they was.

1059
01:19:11,630 --> 01:19:15,341
Gracious, gracious.
You are a good woman, Miz Cooper.

1060
01:19:15,426 --> 01:19:18,010
How you figurin' to raise them two
without a woman?

1061
01:19:18,095 --> 01:19:20,221
The Lord will provide.

1062
01:19:20,305 --> 01:19:22,098
The Lord is merciful.

1063
01:19:22,182 --> 01:19:24,600
Oh, what a day this is.

1064
01:19:24,685 --> 01:19:26,894
And there's little John.

1065
01:19:26,979 --> 01:19:29,689
- What's wrong, John?
- Come to me, boy.

1066
01:19:29,773 --> 01:19:32,567
- What's wrong, John?
- Didn't you hear me, boy?

1067
01:19:32,651 --> 01:19:34,902
John, when your dad says come,
you should mind him.

1068
01:19:34,987 --> 01:19:36,988
He ain't my dad.

1069
01:19:40,325 --> 01:19:42,702
No. And he ain't no preacher neither.

1070
01:19:51,044 --> 01:19:53,921
Just march yourself yonder
to your horse, mister.

1071
01:19:56,967 --> 01:19:58,968
- [ Shotgun Cocks ]
- March, mister! I'm not foolin'!

1072
01:20:02,681 --> 01:20:06,350
All right, but you haven't heard
the last of Harry Powell yet.

1073
01:20:07,853 --> 01:20:10,855
The Lord God Jehovah
will guide my hand in vengeance.

1074
01:20:12,691 --> 01:20:14,358
You devils!

1075
01:20:16,320 --> 01:20:18,029
You Whores of Babylon!

1076
01:20:24,328 --> 01:20:26,537
I'll be back when it's dark!

1077
